  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>一日１０個しか焼かないパンかぁ〜。
この時間じゃもう
売り切れてるんじゃないかな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>They only bake 10 loaves of bread a day, huh?
They're probably sold out
by this time of day, right?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>行くぞ、スタン。
無駄口を叩いている暇はない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Let's go, Stahn. We don't have time for idle talk.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>たとえ限定１個だろうと
僕は必ず手に入れてみせる！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Even if all I can get is a single one,
I will get it no matter what!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
